        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Lead-Free Drinking Water for All Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill reauthorizes through FY2031 and revises the Environmental Protection Agency's grant program for reducing lead in drinking water, including by establishing a deadline for grant recipients to fully replace lead service lines.</p>]]>
        </text>
